Package game.action

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AttackAction
    Special Action for attacking other Actors.
    BuyAction
    BuyAction class is a base class that allow the actor to purchase item
    ConsumeItemAction
    ConsumeItemAction class is a base class that allow the actor to consume item
    DestroyShellAction
    DestroyShellAction class is a allows Actor to have an action to destoy Koopa's shell/ Dormant state in this case, only Koopa will allow actor to have this action
    JumpAction
    JumpAction for actor to retrieve, when possible to Jump on a certain ground
    PickUpCoinAction
    PickUpCoinAction class is a base class that allow the actor to pick up the coin
    ResetAction
    Reset Action to control the overall inheritable reset run with its hot key for display
    SpeakAction
    SpeakAction class is a allows actor to return random (with conditions) statements as outputs in this case, Toad uses SpeakAction
